{"tha-ap156:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap156:0.2":"Bandhujivakavagga ","tha-ap156:0.3":"4 Kakkarupupphapujakattheraapadana ","tha-ap156:1.1":"“Devaputto aham santo, ","tha-ap156:1.2":"pujayim sikhinayakam; ","tha-ap156:1.3":"Kakkarupuppham paggayha, ","tha-ap156:1.4":"buddhassa abhiropayim. ","tha-ap156:2.1":"Ekattimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap156:2.2":"yam pupphamabhiropayim; ","tha-ap156:2.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap156:2.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap156:3.1":"Ito ca navame kappe, ","tha-ap156:3.2":"raja sattuttamo ahum; ","tha-ap156:3.3":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap156:3.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap156:4.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap156:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap156:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap156:5.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma kakkarupupphapujako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap156:6.1":"Kakkarupupphapujakattherassapadanam catuttham. "}